{"type":"message","id":"7ce0ea8e","parentId":"319a6d5a","timestamp":"2026-06-11T09:20:06.059Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the context. The user was told to use HttpCanary (小黄鸟) to capture network requests from \"涨棋网\" (a Go/围棋 ranking website) when doing photo counting (拍照数子). They downloaded it, started capturing, but captured too many packets and can't identify which one is the relevant API request.\n\nThey're asking for help filtering the captured packets to find the specific API call related to the photo board counting feature.\n\n\"涨棋网\" is likely a Chinese Go/围棋 website where you can upload a photo of a Go board and it counts the stones. The user needs to find the API endpoint that handles the photo upload/recognition.\n\nI should help them filter the packets - typically HttpCanary has a search/filter function. The key is to:\n1. Only capture packets when doing the specific action (photo counting)\n2. Filter by domain, keywords, or type\n3. Look for POST requests with image/file uploads","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！HttpCanary 抓了一大堆包，确实眼花。教你几个快速定位的方法：\n\n**方法一：先清空，只抓关键操作**\n\n在 HttpCanary 首页点右上角的垃圾桶 🗑️ 图标清空历史记录 → 然后去涨棋网操作一次拍照数子 → 切回来只看新抓到的几条。\n\n**方法二：过滤域名/关键词**\n\n抓到一堆后，点击底部搜索 🔍 图标，搜：\n- `upload` 或 `image` — 上传图片的关键字\n- `recognize` / `detect` / `识别` / `数子` — 识别相关的\n- 涨棋网的域名（比如 `zhangqi.com` 之类的）\n\n**方法三：看请求类型**\n\n在列表里找 **POST** 请求（不是 GET），而且 Content-Type 是 `multipart/form-data` 或包含 `image/` 的——拍照数子肯定要上传图片，这包特征最明显。\n\n**方法四：按时间排序**\n\n如果包是按时间倒序的，操作完之后最下面几条就是最新的。\n\n---\n\n你先把现有的清了，只做一次拍照数子，然后告诉我抓到了哪些请求（截图或者把 URL 发给我），我帮你看哪个是。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2642,"output":470,"cacheRead":11648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14760,"cost":{"input":0.00036988,"output":0.0001316,"cacheRead":0.000326144,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000827624}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781169599002,"responseId":"1b52