{"type":"message","id":"7ee6cd48","parentId":"b4a1f63a","timestamp":"2026-06-11T09:26:26.296Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user doesn't want to use HttpCanary on their phone and wants a different approach. They initially asked about packet capture related to \"涨棋网\" (a Go/Weiqi website) for \"拍照数子\" (photo counting stones - a feature that uses photo recognition to count Go stones on a board).\n\nLet me think of alternative approaches:\n\n1. **PC-based approach**: Use Fiddler, Charles, or mitmproxy on their computer as a proxy, and have the phone route through it\n2. **Use a different Android app**: Packet Capture (by Grey Shirts) - doesn't need root, uses a local VPN\n3. **Use browser dev tools**: If 涨棋网 works in a browser, just use Chrome/Firefox DevTools Network tab\n4. **Use mitmproxy** on their computer to do MITM\n5. **Use Wireshark** with display filters\n\nSince they said \"换个方法\" and they're on a company network with restricted internet (as mentioned in the earlier context), the best approach might be:\n\n- Use browser Developer Tools (F12 → Network tab) if they access 涨棋网 from a desktop browser - this avoids the downloading issue entirely\n- Or use mitmproxy/Charles on the desktop if they can install it\n\nLet me suggest the browser DevTools approach first since it's the simplest and doesn't require any downloads.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"行，换思路。你在电脑上用浏览器打开涨棋网，操作拍照数子的时候用 **F12 开发者工具**抓，不用装任何软件：\n\n**步骤：**\n1. 用 Chrome/Edge 打开涨棋网\n2. 按 **F12** 打开开发者工具\n3. 点顶部的 **Network（网络）** 标签\n4. 勾上 **Preserve log（保留日志）** — 避免页面跳转后包消失\n5. 去拍照数子，操作一次\n6. Network 面板里会自动出现所有请求\n\n**怎么找：**\n- 点 **Img** 或 **Media** 过滤 — 上传的图片在这里\n- 或者点 **Fetch/XHR** — 接口请求在这里\n- 或者搜索框搜 `upload`、`recognize`、`image`\n\n找到后，右键点那个请求 → **Copy as cURL** 或者 **Copy → Copy link address**，发给我就行。\n\n这个方法零安装零下载，F12 自带的功能。试试？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2752,"output":518,"cacheRead":11648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14918,"cost":{"input":0.00038528000000000005,"output":0.00014504,"cacheRead":0.000326144,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000856464}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781169978196,"responseId":"01402d69-a34f-42a8-81da-cdfdab54d070"}}
