{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6d9c4745d084b3c9bdd5bccab8f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-06-11 17:32 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"76f86145","parentId":"3b8f62ce","timestamp":"2026-06-11T09:32:13.265Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"2a8b8d73","parentId":"76f86145","timestamp":"2026-06-11T09:32:29.377Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying it's a WeChat mini program (微信小程序), so F12 browser devtools won't work. WeChat mini programs run inside the WeChat app. Let me think about how to capture HTTP traffic from a WeChat mini program.\n\nOptions:\n1. **HttpCanary** (小黄鸟) - already mentioned, too many packets\n2. **Proxyman / Charles / Fiddler** on PC - set up as a proxy, then set the phone's WiFi proxy to point to the PC. WeChat mini program traffic would go through the proxy.\n3. **Wireshark** - too low level\n4. **mitmproxy** - command-line MITM proxy\n\nThe user's earlier context said their company network blocks external downloads, so they can't download HttpCanary or other tools. But the user already has HttpCanary installed (they said they used it and got too many packets).\n\nWait, re-reading - the user has HttpCanary on their phone already (they said \"抓的包太多了\" meaning they already used it). So the issue isn't getting the tool, it's filtering the noise.\n\nBut they said \"换一种办法\" (change method) repeatedly, so they want a different approach.\n\nLet me think about alternatives:\n\n1. **Charles / Fiddler on PC** - need to install it, but they can't download\n2. **mitmproxy** - need to install via pip\n3. **proxyman** - Mac only\n4. **Use PC as WiFi proxy** - they need a proxy software\n\nActually wait - the user said company network blocks downloads. But they're on a Windows machine. Let me check if they have Python and could use mitmproxy, or if there's another built-in way.\n\nAnother approach: **Fiddler Classic** (free) or **mitmproxy** (Python, can pip install).\n\nOr even simpler - since it's a WeChat mini program, they could try to use **whistle** or **anyproxy** via npm.\n\nActually, the simplest approach that might work:\n- Use **Fiddler Classic** on Windows (if they can get it)\n- Or **mitmproxy** via `pip install mitmproxy`\n\nBut what about **Proxifier** or **Proxyman**?\n\nWait, actually the most practical approach: the user already has HttpCanary. Maybe I should help them filter better, or suggest a simpler tool.\n\nLet me think about what's available:\n1. The user has a Windows PC and a phone\n2. They can't download external files (company network restriction)\n3. HttpCanary is already installed on the phone but too noisy\n\nAlternative: Use **mitmproxy** - it's a Python package, they might be able to `pip install mitmproxy` since pip often works even on restricted networks (or they might have cached packages).\n\nOr: Use **Fiddler** - but need to download.\n\nActually, since this is about a WeChat mini program \"涨棋网\", and the user has a PC... Another option: they could install the WeChat desktop client and open the mini program there, then use Fiddler/Charles on the desktop to capture the traffic directly.\n\nLet me suggest:\n1. PC 装 Fiddler / mitmproxy 当代理\n2. 手机连上这个代理，所有微信小程序流量经过电脑\n3. 或者直接在 PC 微信里打开小程序，用 Fiddler 抓\n\nBut the download issue... Let me check if pip or npm is available on their machine.\n\nActually, let me just ask what's available and propose practical options.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"微信小程序啊，那换个方式。\n\n既然你有电脑（而且 HttpCanary 包太多不好找），方案如下：\n\n**方案一：用 PC 微信打开小程序 + Fiddler（推荐）**\n1. 电脑装 **PC 版微信**，打开后搜到涨棋网小程序，在里面操作拍照\n2. 电脑装 **Fiddler Classic**（免费的，官网 telerik.com/fiddler/fiddler-classic 下载 — 如果被墙了，我帮你想办法）\n3. 开 Fiddler → Tools → Options → Connections → 勾选 \"Allow remote computers to connect\"\n4. 手机 WiFi 设置代理为电脑的 IP + 端口 8888\n5. 手机上装 Fiddler 的 HTTPS 证书\n6. 再操作一次拍照，Fiddler 里只看 `HTTP CONNECT` 到微信的域名就行，比 HttpCanary 干净很多\n\n**方案二：直接用 `mitmproxy`（不用装额外 GUI）**\n你电脑有 Python 的话：\n```bash\npip install mitmproxy\n```\n然后开代理，手机配代理走电脑，命令行界面更精准。\n\n**方案三：资源解包分析**\n你已经抓到 `zqw.wxapkg` 文件了，可以直接解包看源码，找到 API 地址和参数，都不用抓包：\n```bash\n# 用 nodejs 工具解包\nnpm install -g npminstall   # 或直接用 wxapkg 解析工具\n# 然后反编译看 js 源码里的接口\n```\n\n总结一下：\n- **最快** → 方案三直接解 wxapkg 读源码，找到 API URL\n- **最干净** → 方案一 PC 微信 + Fiddler\n- **最轻量** → 方案二 mitmproxy\n\n你想走哪条路？我都有具体步骤。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":847,"output":1163,"cacheRead":13824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15834,"cost":{"input":0.00011858,"output":0.00032564000000000003,"cacheRead":0.00038707199999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000831292}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781170333266,"responseId":"c454341d-edd9-4068-9b16-ffd7d30fbd8b"}}
