{"type":"message","id":"9145508c","parentId":"42be3423","timestamp":"2026-06-11T09:51:49.739Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! Now I have all the information I need:\n\n**API Endpoints:**\n\nThe `env.js` defines:\n```javascript\nservice: function(t) { return \"\".concat(r.server, \"/mp/api/\").concat(t) },\nwebService: function(t) { return \"\".concat(r.server, \"/api/\").concat(t) },\n```\n\nProduction server: `https://www.zhangqi.com.cn`\nTesting server: `https://weiqi.chb2.cn`\n\n**Key API calls found:**\n\n1. **拍照识棋 - Upload recognize image:**\n   ```javascript\n   // In camera.js, the `recognize` function:\n   a.service.upload(\"image/recognize\", i, {mime: c})\n   ```\n   This translates to: **POST `https://www.zhangqi.com.cn/mp/api/image/recognize`** with multipart upload (file + mime parameter)\n\n2. **举报识别错误 - Report recognition error:**\n   ```javascript\n   a.service.post(\"image/report\", {hash: a.hash})\n   ```\n   POST `https://www.zhangqi.com.cn/mp/api/image/report`\n\nSo the key endpoint for the \"拍照数子\" (photo recognition) feature is:\n\n**`POST https://www.zhangqi.com.cn/mp/api/image/recognize`**\n- Method: multipart upload (wx.uploadFile)\n- File field name: \"file\" (default from the upload function in ajax.js)\n- Form data: `{mime: \"image/jpeg\"}` (or whatever the mime type is)\n- Auth: Bearer token (from `go_chess.token` in localStorage / wx storage)\n\nThe response is: `{boardUrl: \"...\", stones: [...], hash: \"...\"}`\n- `boardUrl`: URL to the board image\n- `stones`: 2D array of stone positions\n- `hash`: hash for the recognition result\n\nLet me now present this to the user clearly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！关键信息全有了：\n\n**服务器地址（当前是正式环境）：**\n- **正式环境：** `https://www.zhangqi.com.cn`\n- **测试环境：** `https://weiqi.chb2.cn`\n\n**拍照识棋 API：**\n\n```http\nPOST https://www.zhangqi.com.cn/mp/api/image/recognize\nContent-Type: multipart/form-data\nHeaders:\n  Authorization: Bearer <token>\n  zhq-client-type: miniprogram.<platform>\n  zhq-client-version: 1.1.272\n\nForm fields:\n  file: <图片文件>\n  mime: image/jpeg (或实际MIME类型)\n```\n\n**返回数据格式：**\n```json\n{\n  \"boardUrl\": \"...\",    // 棋盘图片URL\n  \"stones\": [...],      // 棋子位置二维数组\n  \"hash\": \"...\"         // 识别结果hash\n}\n```\n\n**其他相关 API：**\n- `POST /mp/api/image/report` — 举报识别错误（传 hash）\n- `GET /mp/api/logs/` — 日志上报\n- `GET /api/...` — webService 端（用户、报告等）\n\n**token 存在微信本地存储** key 为 `go_chess.token`，需要通过小程序登录才能拿到（微信登录）。\n\n---\n\n如果你只是想直接调这个接口测试，难点在于 **token** 需要从微信小程序里拿。你有两种办法：\n1. **本地试** — 我写个脚本，你在微信小程序里打开涨棋网 → 在开发者工具或抓包里复制出 token 给我，我直接调 API\n2. **反着来** — 用 HttpCanary 抓一次成功的请求，我帮你解析出 token\n\n想走哪个？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2639,"output":803,"cacheRead":88832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92274,"cost":{"input":0.00036946,"output":0.00022484000000000002,"cacheRead":0.002487296,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003081596}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781171500411,"responseId":"31832264-c937-4cf7-abed-ab95a336fe06"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7387615f","parentId":"9145508c","timestamp":"2026-06-11T09:53:31.875Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6d9c17b790acb03ea3680173a1b]\nYousan(叶枝君): token能通过我们自己的小程序登录以后拿到吗"}],"timestamp":1781171611870}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6d9c17b790acb03ea3680173a1b\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-06-11 17:53 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"1ce4449f","parentId":"7387615f","timestamp":"2026-06-11T09:53:31.876Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"5eff4f14","parentId":"1ce4449f","timestamp":"2026-06-11T09:53:44.100Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if they can get a token for the 涨棋网 API by logging in through their own WeChat mini program. This is a good question.\n\nLet me think about this. The 涨棋网 mini program uses WeChat login (wx.login) to authenticate users. The authentication flow is:\n\n1. Call `wx.login()` to get a `code`\n2. Send the `code` to the 涨棋网 backend (`https://www.zhangqi.com.cn/api/login` or similar)\n3. The backend exchanges the code for a session key and returns a custom token\n4. The token is stored as `go_chess.token` in WeChat local storage\n\nThe question is: can we get a token using our own mini program?\n\n**If】** we have our own registered mini program with its own appid:\n- We CAN call `wx.login()` to get a code\n- But the code is tied to OUR appid, not 涨棋网's appid\n- When we send that code to 涨棋网's backend (`https://www.zhangqi.com.cn/api/login`), the backend will try to exchange it with WeChat servers\n- WeChat servers will verify that the code matches the appid that was used to generate it\n- Since 涨棋网's backend uses THEIR appid/secret, not ours, the exchange will **FAIL**\n- So this approach won't work\n\n**Alternative approaches:**\n1. We could look at the login API endpoint in the decompiled code and see if there's a simpler way\n2. We could look at what the login API expects\n3. We could set up a proxy/mitm to intercept the token when using the real mini program\n\nLet me look at the decompiled code for the login/user API to understand the auth flow better.\n\nActually, let me search for the login or auth related code in the decompiled files.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"理论上不行，让我看看源码里登录是怎么做的，确认一下。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_0IPOxwcDWdOd209QlHCy4902","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"const fs = require('fs');\nconst path = require('path');\nconst root = 'C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\Downloads\\\\小程序解包\\\\涨棋网';\n\nconst fp = path.join(root, 'app-service.js');\nconst content = fs.readFileSync(fp, 'utf8');\nconst lines = content.split('\\n');\n\n// Find user.js or login-related code\nconsole.log('=== Searching for login/auth in app.js (line 186) ===');\nconsole.log(lines[185].substring(0, 1000));\n\n// Find the user module  \nfor (let i = 0; i < lines.length; i++) {\n  if (lines[i].includes('utils/user') && lines[i].includes('login')) {\n    console.log(`\\n=== User module at line ${i+1} ===`);\n    console.log(lines[i].substring(0, 800));\n  }\n}\n\n// Search for wx.login\nfor (let i = 0; i < lines.length; i++) {\n  if (lines[i].includes('wx.login') || lines[i].includes('login')) {\n    console.log(`\\n=== wx.login/auth at line ${i+1} ===`);\n    console.log(lines[i].substring(0, 600));\n    break;\n  }\n}\n\n// Search for getToken or setToken\nconsole.log('\\n=== Searching for token handling ===');\nfor (let i = 0; i < lines.length; i++) {\n  if (lines[i].includes('go_chess.token') || (lines[i].includes('setToken') || lines[i].includes('getToken'))) {\n    console.log(`L${i+1}: ${lines[i].substring(0, 500)}`);\n  }\n}\n\n// Look for login POST endpoint\nconsole.log('\\n=== Searching for login API path ===');\nfor (let i = 0; i < lines.length; i++) {\n  if (lines[i].includes('/login') || lines[i].includes('/auth') || lines[i].includes('/token') || lines[i].includes('/session')) {\n    console.log(`L${i+1}: ${lines[i].substring(0, 400)}`);\n  }\n}\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\find_login.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":33808,"output":950,"cacheRead":32768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67526,"cost":{"input":0.00473312,"output":0.000266,"cacheRead":0.000917504,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0059166240000000005}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781171611876,"responseId":"89ca19cd-b96e-4ba7-b874-05f651ec8d6a"}}
