{"type":"message","id":"90800997","parentId":"901a3924","timestamp":"2026-06-11T09:54:11.150Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I found the exact login flow:\n\n```javascript\nlogin: function() {\n  return t(e().mark(function t() {\n    var r, i;\n    return e().wrap(function(e) {\n      switch(e.prev = e.next) {\n        case 0: return e.prev = 0, e.next = 3, wx.login();\n        case 3: return r = e.sent, e.next = 6, a.service.post(\"user/login\", {\n          code: r.code,\n          systemInfo: n.globalData.systemInfo,\n          options: n.launchOptions,\n          id: o.getLastId()\n        });\n        case 6: i = e.sent, n.onUserLogin(i), e.next = 20; break;\n        ...\n      }\n    })\n  }))\n}\n```\n\nSo the login endpoint is:\n\n**POST `https://www.zhangqi.com.cn/mp/api/user/login`** (or testing: `https://weiqi.chb2.cn/mp/api/user/login`)\n\n**Request body:**\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": \"<wx.login code>\",\n  \"systemInfo\": { \"...\", \"platform\": \"miniprogram\", \"version\": \"1.1.272\" },\n  \"options\": \"<launch options>\",\n  \"id\": \"<last user id>\"\n}\n```\n\nNow to answer the user's question: Can we log in through their own mini program to get a token?\n\nThe answer is: **No, it won't work directly.**\n\nHere's why:\n1. `wx.login()` generates a `code` that is bound to YOUR mini program's `appid`\n2. That `code` is sent to 涨棋网's backend at `user/login`\n3. 涨棋网's backend calls WeChat's `code2session` API with THEIR `appid` and `secret`\n4. WeChat validates that the `code` was issued for THEIR `appid`, not yours\n5. If the appids don't match, the exchange **fails**\n\nHowever, there ARE some alternative approaches I can suggest:\n\n1. **Use your own backend as a proxy** - If you set up a server that:\n   - Accepts the code from the client\n   - Forwards it to 涨棋网's API as-is\n   \n   ...this still won't work because the code is bound to your appid.\n\n2. **Use the HttpCanary token directly** - If they captured at least one successful request, they can extract the token\n\n3. **Run the mini program in a controlled environment** (PC WeChat DevTools) and intercept the token\n\n4. **Try calling the API without auth** - some endpoints might be unauthenticated\n\n5. **Use a web-based approach** - The 涨棋网 website at zhangqi.com.cn might use a different auth mechanism\n\nLet me suggest these options to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了登录流程。API 如下：\n\n```http\nPOST https://www.zhangqi.com.cn/mp/api/user/login\nBody:\n{\n  \"code\": \"<wx.login() 的临时 code>\",\n  \"systemInfo\": {...},\n  \"options\": {...},\n  \"id\": \"<上次登录的用户ID>\"\n}\n```\n\n**回答你的问题：用我们自己的小程序拿不到 token。**\n\n原因是微信的 `wx.login()` 拿到的 `code` 是跟**你的小程序 appid 绑定**的。涨棋网后端收到 code 后会用**他们的 appid + secret** 去微信服务器换 session，微信那边会校验 code 是否匹配他们的 appid，不匹配就失败。\n\n所以这条路走不通。替代方案：\n\n1. **直接用 HttpCanary 抓一次** — 你之前说包太多，教你一招：只保留登录那几秒的包，搜 `user/login` 的 response，里面就有 token\n2. **PC 微信打开涨棋小程序** — 用 Fiddler 或 mitmproxy 代理抓包，也能拿到 token\n3. **试试无 token 能不能调** — 有些小程序拍照识别的接口可能对游客开放（不用登录也能用），我可以试试直接 POST 一下\n4. **浏览器试** — `www.zhangqi.com.cn` 网页端也有拍照数子功能吗？如果有那可能是另一种鉴权方式\n\n你觉得哪种比较可行？如果想试试第 3 种，我现在就直接调一下那个 API 看看返回什么。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":690,"output":937,"cacheRead":76416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78043,"cost":{"input":0.0000966,"output":0.00026236,"cacheRead":0.002139648,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0024986080000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781171640525,"responseId":"aef67628-9723-478b-aff6-adff6374af08"}}
