{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6d9c102f44acb3b7c16c1085438\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-06-11 17:54 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"7297f548","parentId":"ba0d4600","timestamp":"2026-06-11T09:54:58.431Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"60bf2712","parentId":"7297f548","timestamp":"2026-06-11T09:55:05.963Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to try option 3 - make a POST request to the API without a token to see if it works for unauthenticated users.\n\nThe API endpoint is:\n- POST `https://www.zhangqi.com.cn/mp/api/image/recognize` (production)\n- POST `https://weiqi.chb2.cn/mp/api/image/recognize` (testing - might be more permissive)\n\nBut wait - this is a file upload endpoint (multipart/form-data), not a simple JSON POST. I need to have an actual image file to test with.\n\nLet me think about what I can do here. The upload uses `wx.uploadFile()` which in the code sends:\n- `filePath`: the image file\n- `name`: \"file\" (default in the upload function)\n- `formData`: `{mime: \"image/jpeg\"}`\n\nI don't have an actual Go board photo to send. But I could try sending the API a request without a token to see what error it returns - this would tell us if auth is required or not.\n\nLet me first try hitting the API with a simple request to see what happens. I could try:\n1. A GET request to see if it responds\n2. A POST with empty data to see the error message  \n3. A POST with a small test image\n\nActually, let me try both the production and testing servers to see which one responds. Let me also try the recognize endpoint with and without token.\n\nBut wait - this is a multipart file upload. I need to send an actual image. Let me create a small test image and try uploading it.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，先试试直接调 API 看看要不要 token。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Qpls1LJMLVRWqB0Pwv099378","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; node -e \"\nconst https = require('https');\n\n// Try hitting the production server first\nfunction testGet(url) {\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n    const req = https.get(url, {timeout: 10000}, (res) => {\n      let data = '';\n      res.on('data', chunk => data += chunk);\n      res.on('end', () => {\n        resolve({status: res.statusCode, headers: res.headers, body: data.substring(0, 500)});\n      });\n    });\n    req.on('error', reject);\n    req.on('timeout', () => { req.destroy(); reject(new Error('timeout')); });\n  });\n}\n\n(async () => {\n  console.log('=== Testing production server ===');\n  try {\n    const r = await testGet('https://www.zhangqi.com.cn/mp/api/image/recognize');\n    console.log('Status:', r.status);\n    console.log('Headers:', JSON.stringify(r.headers, null, 2));\n    console.log('Body:', r.body);\n  } catch(e) { console.log('Error:', e.message); }\n  \n  console.log('\\n=== Testing testing server ===');\n  try {\n    const r = await testGet('https://weiqi.chb2.cn/mp/api/image/recognize');\n    console.log('Status:', r.status);\n    console.log('Headers:', JSON.stringify(r.headers, null, 2));\n    console.log('Body:', r.body);\n  } catch(e) { console.log('Error:', e.message); }\n})();\n\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":12549,"output":756,"cacheRead":65536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78841,"cost":{"input":0.00175686,"output":0.00021168,"cacheRead":0.001835008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003803548}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781171698431,"responseId":"64bff749-455f-4691-a2de-2adfc30ed994"}}
