{"type":"message","id":"3b23832b","parentId":"c26a932d","timestamp":"2026-06-11T09:55:49.792Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ET_k74kKoGOx6uGcBV0gZt69068","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 1. POST multipart to production (no token) ===\nStatus: 401 Body: {\"message\":\"Unauthorized\"}\n\n=== 2. POST JSON to production (no token) ===\nStatus: 401 Body: {\"message\":\"Unauthorized\"}\n\n=== 3. Login API with fake code ===\nStatus: 500 Body: {}\n\n=== 4. Testing server multipart ===\nStatus: 401 Body: {\"message\":\"Unauthorized\"}\n\n=== 5. GET homepage ===\nStatus: 405 Body: <html>\r\n<head><title>405 Not Allowed</title></head>\r\n<body bgcolor=\"white\">\r\n<center><h1>405 Not Allowed</h1></center>\r\n<hr><center>nginx/1.6.2</center>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n\n\n=== 6. Try common API paths ===\n/api/v1/recognize -> Status: 401 Body: Unauthorized\n/api/recognize -> Status: 401 Body: Unauthorized\n/api/upload -> Status: 401 Body: Unauthorized\n/mp/api/v1/image/recognize -> Status: 404 Body: {\"message\":\"Not Found\"}\n\n=== 7. Try with zhq-client-type header set to miniprogram ===\nStatus: 401 Body: {\"message\":\"Unauthorized\"}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":819,"aggregated":"=== 1. POST multipart to production (no token) ===\nStatus: 401 Body: {\"message\":\"Unauthorized\"}\n\n=== 2. POST JSON to production (no token) ===\nStatus: 401 Body: {\"message\":\"Unauthorized\"}\n\n=== 3. Login API with fake code ===\nStatus: 500 Body: {}\n\n=== 4. Testing server multipart ===\nStatus: 401 Body: {\"message\":\"Unauthorized\"}\n\n=== 5. GET homepage ===\nStatus: 405 Body: <html>\r\n<head><title>405 Not Allowed</title></head>\r\n<body bgcolor=\"white\">\r\n<center><h1>405 Not Allowed</h1></center>\r\n<hr><center>nginx/1.6.2</center>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n\n\n=== 6. Try common API paths ===\n/api/v1/recognize -> Status: 401 Body: Unauthorized\n/api/recognize -> Status: 401 Body: Unauthorized\n/api/upload -> Status: 401 Body: Unauthorized\n/mp/api/v1/image/recognize -> Status: 404 Body: {\"message\":\"Not Found\"}\n\n=== 7. Try with zhq-client-type header set to miniprogram ===\nStatus: 401 Body: {\"message\":\"Unauthorized\"}","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781171749792}}
{"type":"message","id":"15b24254","parentId":"3b23832b","timestamp":"2026-06-11T09:55:54.692Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Results are clear:\n- The `image/recognize` API requires authentication (401 Unauthorized)\n- The login API returns 500 with a fake code (expected - the code is invalid)\n- All non-authenticated API paths return 401\n\nSo option 3 didn't work - all the image recognition APIs require a valid token.\n\nNow the options are:\n1. **Use HttpCanary** - filter by `user/login` response to find token\n2. **PC WeChat + Fiddler** - proxy the PC WeChat client\n3. **Web version** - the website at `www.zhangqi.com.cn` might work via browser with different auth\n\nLet me suggest next steps.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"结果很明确——**所有 API 都要 token，没 token 全部 401 Unauthorized。** 登录接口发假 code 返回 500。\n\n所以必须拿到真实 token。推荐的下一步：\n\n**最快的办法：用 HttpCanary 只抓登录包**\n\n操作步骤：\n1. 打开 HttpCanary → 点右下角垃圾桶 🗑️ 清空所有记录\n2. 打开涨棋小程序 → 强制重启（手机划掉后台重新打开），因为每次启动都会调 `user/login`\n3. 切回 HttpCanary，你应该只会看到几条包\n4. 搜 `user/login` → 点开看 **响应（Response）**，里面就有 token\n\n或者你告诉我 HttpCanary 抓包时，你认不认得哪个是 `user/login` 的请求？我指导你精准定位。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":349,"output":328,"cacheRead":84992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85669,"cost":{"input":0.00004886,"output":0.00009184,"cacheRead":0.002379776,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0025204760000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781171749793,"responseId":"f8e8ee81-37ba-4cdd-a863-c74d3fa0b9e7"}}
