urn h.apply(this,arguments)},l.setLastId=v,l.getLastId=function(){return wx.getStorageSync(\"go_chess.user_id\")||0};var g=[],m=[],b=[];function h(){return(h=r(t().mark((function r(){var n,a,i,o,u,c,f,v,p,d,h,k,w,y,x,S,U,q,A;return t().wrap((function(t){for(;;)switch(t.prev=t.next){case 0:return t.next=2,s.webService.get(\"user/current\");case 2:n=t.sent,a={},i=Object.keys(n).filter((function(e){return e.toLowerCase().includes(\"taste_\")})),g=Array.from(new Set(g.concat(i))),o=e(g);try{for(o.s();!(u=o.n()).done;)f=u.value,a[f]=null!==(c=n[f])&&void 0!==c&&c}catch(e){o.e(e)}\n\n=== All API endpoints mentioned in code ===\n  image/jpeg\n  image/png\n  image/recognize\n  image/report\n  log/route\n  logs/grow\n  logs/review\n  logs/video\n  user/avatar\n  user/current\n  user/current/certifications\n  user/current/setting\n  user/current/todo\n  user/list\n  user/load\n  user/login\n  user/nick\n  user/rank\n  user/settings\n  user/subscribe\n  user/switch\n  user/task/ignore\n  user/tasks\n  user/taste/grow","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781171824780}}
{"type":"message","id":"2e4a3fca","parentId":"d547f261","timestamp":"2026-06-11T09:57:14.165Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Key finding from `onUserLogin`:\n\n```javascript\nonUserLogin: function(n) {\n  var i = this;\n  return t(e().mark(function t() {\n    return e().wrap(function(e) {\n      for(;;) switch(e.prev = e.next) {\n        case 0:\n          if (!n.mode) { e.next = 6; break }\n          ...\n      }\n    })\n  }))\n}\n```\n\nAnd from `onLoginFail`:\n```javascript\nonLoginFail: function() {\n  var e = this;\n  setTimeout(function() { return e.login() }, ...)\n}\n```\n\nSo `onLoginFail` retries login after a timeout.\n\nThe token behavior:\n1. Token is stored in `go_chess.token` (wx storage)\n2. The app always reads saved token first: `d(wx.getStorageSync(\"go_chess.token\"))`\n3. Login is called on every `onLaunch`\n4. If login fails, it retries\n\nThe token **doesn't seem to have an explicit expiry mechanism in the client code**. However:\n\n1. It's a JWT-like token (from the backend)\n2. The server handles expiry (returns 401 when expired)\n3. If a request returns unauthorized, the mini program would try to re-login\n\nFrom the `onUserLogin` code, it receives `n` (the login response) which contains `.mode`. The login response likely contains:\n- `token` or the response itself is the token\n- `mode` - some mode flag\n\nLooking at the setToken function: `d(e)` sets `i.Authorization = e` where `e` is the parameter passed to `onUserLogin` (the login response). So the entire login response data IS the token (or at least it's stored as-is).\n\nSo to answer the user's question about token expiry:\n\nFrom the code, I can't see an explicit expiry time. But typical WeChat mini program tokens:\n- **Most common**: Session tokens last about **24 hours** (微信 session_key 有效期)\n- **Some**: Custom tokens last longer (7 days or more)\n- The app re-logs in on every launch, suggesting the token CAN persist across sessions\n\nLet me give the user a practical answer.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"从源码分析来看，token 有效期的情况：\n\n**客户端看不到明确的过期时间**，但有几个关键线索：\n\n1. **每次启动都重新登录** — `onLaunch` 里调 `this.login()`，说明 token 可能不是长期有效的\n2. **登录失败会自动重试** — `onLoginFail` 里 `setTimeout(() => this.login(), ...)` \n3. **token 存在微信本地存储** — key `go_chess.token`，退出小程序不清除\n\n**业内惯例推测：**\n- 涨棋网用的应该是微信 `session_key` 机制，有效期 **通常 24 小时**（最长 7 天）\n- 但每次打开小程序都会 `wx.login()` 重新拿 code → 换新 token，旧 token 可能立即失效\n\n**实际建议：**\n\n你现在抓一次登录的响应，把 token 拿到手后直接用。即使有效期短，也足够一次性调 `image/recognize` 来测试了。如果过期了重新抓一次就行。\n\n要不你现在试一下 **HttpCanary 清空后重开涨棋小程序**，看看能不能抓到 `user/login` 的包？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":533,"output":721,"cacheRead":89344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90598,"cost":{"input":0.00007462,"output":0.00020188,"cacheRead":0.0025016319999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0027781319999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781171824782,"responseId":"ca811acd-0f35-4f4c-b0fc-57c0f916db89"}}
